Class Method

java.lang.Object
  ast.ASTNode
      ast.Member
          ast.Method

public class Method
extends Member

The Method class represents a method declaration within a class declaration. It contains the name of the method (name), a list of formal parameters (formalList), the return type of the method (returnType), a list of statements from the method body (stmtList), and a return statement at the end of the method body (returnStmt).
